{"tid":580280,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"做左D破格野, 比老豆屌到飛起","createTime":"2018-03-04T11:21:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-05T04:55:43.000Z","uid":35361,"like":10,"dislike":69,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"669154c3faa9e3f14335f7f7241f3a81e644391a","tid":580280,"uid":35361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T11:21:35.000Z","msg":"我係係大家姐, 有細佬2個 呀妹1個, 咁平時大家都有零用錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我都著量收返D佢地既零用錢(30%左右), 為日後應急用 都係一D長遠既計劃 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但暑假果時老豆唔知係咪發左達 無啦啦加我地零用 仲要加左幾多下, 所以到年頭收返黎條數大左好多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  班細路係咁話要派錢, 好撚煩<br />\n<br />\n咁我咪話: 計劃要長遠, 唔係派錢就得, 咁但係我都要做返D野, 所以我用左D錢幫細佬妹代交班會費, 又額外幫每人放左$200入呀媽管既補習基金<br />\n<br />\n但係最細既妹讀緊小學, 未有班會, 係咁係度嘈 話唔公平 真係好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77d5d61dabbca751ff07c4f656f31adf56ea774d","tid":580280,"uid":46328,"like":2,"dislike":15,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T11:23:31.000Z","msg":"有冇做埋右？"},{"pid":"63007f82865c4f6839e0d0abf35734a6a6aefbbb","tid":580280,"uid":35361,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"77d5d61dabbca751ff07c4f656f31adf56ea774d","tid":580280,"uid":46328,"like":2,"dislike":15,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T11:23:31.000Z","msg":"有冇做埋右？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T11:23:52.000Z","msg":"做左就唔洗比人屌啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcb4a3e444b323b5496c19463281c4ab9c9c700c","tid":580280,"uid":174353,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T11:24:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9e108ee485